{
  "stem": "26888.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, that meant a lot to survive, because it was awful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You couldn't survive if you didn't have a little bit from here or there, you know, a little bit of food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So even when we we're marching, six days and six nights.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the first three days, one German said that he's going to cook for us, potatoes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, he had those animals there, the cows with the pigs, things like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that thing he cooked for us, those potatoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he made place for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He has a big place, he made place for us to sleep on the floor, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, um, uh- but potatoes, who wants to bring the potatoes?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he had to bring it because it was somewhere else where they were cooked.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they pick.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I was running to help out, you know, meanwhile I was stuffing myself with potatoes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I was so hot, I was burning my, my-- yeah, and fell down, you know, and because the overalls were closed so it fell down at my feet.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And here-- and I had-- and I ate there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I ate three potatoes they gave or something, so I had a lot more than anybody else, because I had potatoes here and I had potatoes there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also my sister, my sister was-- if she wouldn't be with me, she wouldn't be alive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's for sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I actually took it for her and for myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had-- and the other- and at night, that was when we came, at night, we had those potatoes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After that, we decided we were always five people together, three sisters and me and my sister.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We tried to be together.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
